Privacy policy for BetBudd

At [BetBudd], we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is secure. This privacy policy ("Policy") explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our BetBudd application ("Application") available on the App Store.

By using our Application, you agree to the collection, use, and sharing of your information as described in this Policy. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, do not use our Application.

We use third-party advertising services, such as Google AdMob, to serve advertisements on our Application. These services may collect information about your use of our Application and other websites and online services, and may use cookies, web beacons, and other tracking technologies to track your online activity. The information collected by these services is used to personalize the advertisements you see and to measure the effectiveness of our advertising campaigns. However, we do not share any personal information with these services.

We will not sell, rent, or share your personal information with any third parties for their marketing purposes without your consent.

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at [danieljermaine1@gmail.com].

We may update this Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this Policy whenever you access our Application to understand how we collect, use, and share your information.
